<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sideways-adv">sideways <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'saɪdweɪz/    美 /'saɪdweɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>斜向旁边；侧着身子：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you would move sideways to the left, I can get everyone in the picture.
如果你向左边侧一下身子，我就能把所有人都拍进去。</p></div></div>